title: BRIEF-Talex gets orders from Credit Agricole Bank Polska
text:
BRIEF-Talex gets orders from Credit Agricole Bank Polska 
Oct 12 Talex SA : 
* Since April 7 got orders from Credit Agricole Bank Polska for delivery of IT services for total value of 5.62 million zlotys ($1.5 million) net Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7080 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
